be used to:

  a) create or augment datasets;
  b) train, fine-tune, evaluate or test machine-learning or generative-AI
     models;
  c) create embeddings, vector indexes, RAG stores or other AI indexes;
  d) submit or paste Author Materials into an external AI service, coding
     assistant or automated-analysis system; or
  e) generate, reconstruct or develop a competing program or solution from
